text: Vilseck is a town in Amberg-Sulzbach, a district (Landkreis) in the Upper Palatinate. It is on the river Vils, which is a tributary of the Naab river. == References == == Other websites == * Information about Grafenwoehr and the area * Information about Rose Barracks, Vilseck Category:Amberg-Sulzbach
